flowRoot.flowPara: TO ANALYZE OR NOT TO ANALYZE?
To save time in the long run, make sure to thoroughly address each of the following before commencing a new analysis of your dataset.
WHY AM I PERFORMING THIS ANALYSIS?
CAN I EXPLAIN MY ANALYSIS PROCEDURE TO OTHERS IN MY FIELD?
HOW WILL I CHOOSE MY PARAMETERS?
HOW WILL I ASSESS STATISTICAL SIGNIFICANCE?
HOW LONG WILL IT TAKE TO PERFORM MY ANALYSIS?
HOW WILL I VERIFY THE CORRECTNESS OF MY CODE?
HOW WILL I INTEGRATE MY NEW CODE INTO MY EXISTING CODEBASE?
HOW WILL I STORE MY RESULTS?
HOW IS MY ANALYSIS MOST LIKELY TO FAIL?
HOW CAN I SIMPLIFY MY ANALYSIS?
HOW WILL I VISUALIZE MY RESULTS?
WHAT ASPECTS OF MY ANALYSIS HAVE I NOT YET FIGURED OUT?
